&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Food Safety &amp;amp; Quality Checks - continually evaluate products (WIP, FGs, ingredients) to ensure compliance with DG quality standards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Equipment Quality Checks - continually evaluate production equipment to ensure consistency and safety in output&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Process Confirmation - ensure quality and food safety processes are in place and active across the floor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
